{
  "3238940": {
    "name": "和存在感薄弱的妹妹一起的简单生活",
    "steam_appid": 3238940,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/3fd6fecf3c60b9428172e9c92ee31c51.poster.avif?t=1771397097\" width=780 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/3fd6fecf3c60b9428172e9c92ee31c51.webm?t=1771397097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——如今已是距离魔王被勇者讨伐过去了很多年的时代。曾经声名远扬的勇者和贤者,他们的传说如今也不过成了大人用来教训小孩的童话罢了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「深渊」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是对十年前突然出现的谜之大型迷宫的称呼。它有着似乎无穷无尽的深度，星罗棋布的遗迹，以及受到魔力滋养而快速繁殖的魔物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险者曾多次组队深入其中，却始终没有取得决定性的进展。这座迷宫也从未对外展现过侵略或反击的意图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最终，关于深渊的一切都随着时间被人们遗忘，除你之外的冒险者们也不再踏足此处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而治愈妹妹疾病的唯一线索“红髓液”，就藏在深渊之底。那你是仍坚持每日探索深渊的动力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了守护和妹妹一起度过的日常，为了每天在家中静静等待你凯旋归来的妹妹的笑容——你决心征服深渊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/bacf2cd4153adef1e62c76ed3477ead1.poster.avif?t=1771397097\" width=780 height=119 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/bacf2cd4153adef1e62c76ed3477ead1.webm?t=1771397097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款以妹妹日常为核心的生活模拟游戏。所有场景都采用手绘动画演出、妹妹的每一句台词都有配音！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在家里你可以做饭、和妹妹聊天、一起看动画和玩游戏、叫妹妹起床、刷牙、洗澡……有多到惊人的生活场景！所有玩法都是高自由度的SLG模式，所有事件都会随着和妹妹的好感度提升而发生循序渐进的细腻变化！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在深渊中也不仅仅只有战斗，发生的事件、找到的物品都将与和妹妹一起的生活发生联动，让玩法更加丰富多彩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/74a4e73522cc7301760087d723633119.poster.avif?t=1771397097\" width=780 height=522 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/74a4e73522cc7301760087d723633119.webm?t=1771397097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/0eafebf0f7d88c125d4ed1f148bd42da.poster.avif?t=1771397097\" width=780 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/0eafebf0f7d88c125d4ed1f148bd42da.webm?t=1771397097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/02bbb187da2127bb3de592b52fc73842.poster.avif?t=1771397097\" width=780 height=119 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/02bbb187da2127bb3de592b52fc73842.webm?t=1771397097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与妹妹的日常</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险归来后,你将与妹妹享受难得的温馨时光——用从深渊收集到的食材做饭、畅谈冒险故事、和妹妹一起玩游戏和看电视，或者并肩小憩。作为养成系游戏,你可以细致观察妹妹的成长,感受作为哥哥的成就感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而随着和妹妹变得更亲密,还能解锁更多互动！几乎所有事件都会随着和妹妹的好感度提升而发生循序渐进的细腻变化！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动画表现</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由在推特拥有84万粉丝的知名插画师逆流茶会绘制了大量手绘动画，拥有与live2d动画、静态CG截然不同的生动表现力！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>语音演出</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妹妹的所有台词都有配音。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike 与开放世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次进入深渊，地形、敌人、宝物等都会发生小小的变化，提供无尽的重玩价值和挑战。你需要在每次探索中</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >学习和适应,才能更深入地挖掘深渊的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ACT 实时战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用了使用键盘和鼠标的即时战斗模式，你可以通过组合技能和装备获取全新的战斗体验。深渊每一层的挑战都是独一无二的，你需要灵活运用战术和技能才能取得胜利。随着深入探索,你可以解锁新的技能和装备，更多的配装思路也就意味着更多的可能性和更强大的战斗力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/db152c9ede1d112bc377c6d22114d099.poster.avif?t=1771397097\" width=780 height=311 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238940/extras/db152c9ede1d112bc377c6d22114d099.webm?t=1771397097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
